Product Overview
















		
	
		CUSTOM COUNTERTOP INSTALLATION
		
	
		










		
	
		What to Consider Before You Buy
		
	
		











			Your dream, our expertise:  Your custom countertop will be professionally installed by the Home Depot’s industry experts.If you are interested in letting us help transform your kitchen with a new custom countertop, start with the easy-to-use Countertop Estimator.  Here, you can choose your material and color, get an estimate for your project, and set an appointment with one of our in-store designers.










		
	
		3 Steps to Expert Installation
		
	
		














		
	
		1. Get a Price Estimate Now
		
	
		







			Use this tool to calculate the estimated price of the perfect countertop for your taste and budget.  Expert installation is included in pricing.  Use our Live Chat feature any time of day for prompt, professional assistance.
		
	



















		
	
		2. Meet with a Designer In-Store
		
	
		







			Our knowledgeable designers will walk you through showroom samples, offer professional advice, and assist you with your final purchase.
		
	










		
	
		3. Transform Your Kitchen
		
	
		







			Have the peace of mind that professional installers backed by the Home Depot will get the job done right.
		
	


























				            Stonemark Granite is exclusive to The Home Depot. Stonemark products are 100% natural granite. All Stonemark Granite treated with StoneGuard sealer is resistant to food and beverage stains. Stonemark Granite treated with StoneGuard are backed by a limited 15 year warranty that covers material integrity defects and food and beverage staining, Pitting, veining and fissures are natural to all real granite, creating a unique character of natural stone. Upgrade your kitchen today with Stonemark. Stonemark Granite slabs are hand-picked for each job. The color and grain can differ from sample slab. This variation is inherent to all granite and is part of the unique character of natural stone. Slab viewing may be available, ask your fabricator for details.
				        

Bring your sample receipt to your local Home Depot store for a credit toward your granite countertop purchase
15 year limited warranty against food and beverage staining
Fabricator sealed with StoneGuard and applied in a controlled environment
Supported by, licensed, insured and background-checked fabricator network
Stonemark Granite sold in square feet increments, sampled as 3 in. x 3 in. swatch
Bring your sample receipt to your local Home Depot store for a credit toward your carpet purchase
All-natural product and varies in shading and coloring; for more information please contact a home depot near you!
Start your kitchen design today with our Kitchen Planner
Get a free quote with our Countertop Estimator

 




 




